description:
Aaron Rodgers (0:06) talks about how relaxing the offseason has been. Matt Nagy (1:18) says Andy Dalton is still the man. Calvin Ridley (1:34) not feeling the pressure in Atlanta. Tua Tagovailoa (2:42) talks about his rough day at minicamp. TJ Watt (3:11) not motivated by defensive MVP snub. Derek Carr (3:57) says he's a Raider for life
